{
  "stem": "802.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was very difficult, because Jews didn't have quite the same recourse to law, as I remember it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I haven't studied it, and I may perhaps not present it in the most accurate way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But as I knew it, Jews didn't have the same kind of recourse to the courts of law, to law in general, as the Poles.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You may know the fact that when a Jew went to the university, even to high school, he had to bring a Gentile with him, otherwise he would not be admitted to the university, or even to high school.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that was before.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was before the period during which I was born.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I really don't know-- during which I lived, I should say.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I don't really know what the nature of education was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I think more Jews were allowed a greater freedom to go to school without having to bring a Polish student with them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know whether it's clear to you what I mean to bring-- to make sure that a Polish student gets also an education.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was incumbent upon the Jewish student to make sure that he encourages a Polish one to go, you know, to college or high school, as far as I know.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know this to be a fact.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, this is not hearsay.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just don't know the precise time, what it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think it was during the time that I was growing up, but I think it was before.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So certainly, this is not an area of expertise for me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What were some of the first signs to you that anti-Semitism and danger to Jews were escalating?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1939-- '36, '37, German Jews were expelled from Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
